What you need to know:  Upon the expiry of the 40-day mourning period, the Kalenjin Council of Elders (Myoot) in Uasin Gishu will congregate at Mzee Jackson Kibor’s Samitui home to offer cleansing prayers at the site where the Azimio la Umoja-One Kenya Alliance leaders were attacked.They expressed remorse over the incident and asked for forgiveness from Mr Odinga and his entourage on behalf of the Kalenjin community.